    "Once the data has been preprocessed, an optimal subset of features is derived using the FD.",
    "The GBSO is then utilised to further optimise the FD and decrease classification time while improving accuracy.",
    "In order to predict abnormalities in the provided EEG signal, the classification is ultimately carried out using the TAENN algorithm.",
